<section class="gradient-form">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
      <div class="col-xl-10">
        <div class="card rounded-3 text-black">
          <div class="row g-0">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <div class="card-body p-md-5 mx-md-4">
                <div class="text-center">
                  <img src="https://mdbcdn.b-cdn.net/img/Photos/new-templates/bootstrap-login-form/lotus.webp"
                    style="width: 185px;" alt="logo">
                  <h4 class="mt-1 mb-5 pb-1">We Are The Durgesh Team Member</h4>
                </div>

                <!-- Login Form -->
                <form action="/login" method="post">
                  <p>Please log in to your account</p>

                  <!-- Username (Email or Phone Number) input -->
                  <div class="form-outline mb-1">
                    <input type="text" id="form2Example11" class="form-control" name="email"
                      placeholder="Phone number or email address" required/>
                    <label class="form-label" for="form2Example11">Username</label>
                  </div>

                  <!-- Password input with a Show button -->
                  <div class="form-outline mb-1">
                    <input type="password" id="passInput" name="password" class="form-control" required/>
                    <label class="form-label" for="form2Example22">Password</label>
                    <button class="mt-1 password-button btn btn-outline-secondary" type="button"
                      id="PassButton">Show</button>
                  </div>

                  <div class="text-center pt-1 mb-2 mt-3 pb-1">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block fa-lg gradient-custom-2 mb-3 p-3" type="submit">Log
                      in</button>
                    <a class="text-muted" href="/signup">Forgot password?</a>
                  </div>
                </form>

                <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center pb-4">
                  <p class="mb-0 me-2">Don't have an account?</p>
                  <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-outline-danger">Create new</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Right column with additional information -->
            <div class="col-lg-6 d-flex align-items-center gradient-custom-2">
              <div class="text-white px-3 py-4 p-md-5 mx-md-4">
                <h4 class="mb-4">We are more than just a company</h4>
                <p class="mediam mb-0">Hello Team,

I hope this message finds you all well. As members of the Durgesh team, we've accomplished some great things together, and I want to take a moment to appreciate each and every one of you for your dedication and hard work.

In our journey together, we've faced challenges and celebrated successes, and I believe that our teamwork has been the key to our achievements. As we continue to work towards our goals, let's remember the importance of collaboration, communication, and supporting one another.

Our collective efforts have brought us this far, and I have no doubt that we have the potential to achieve even greater heights in the future. So, let's stay focused, stay motivated, and keep pushing towards our objectives.

If anyone has any ideas, concerns, or suggestions, please don't hesitate to share them. Our team's success depends on open and constructive communication.

Thank you for being part of the Durgesh team and for all that you do. Together, we are unstoppable!

Warm regards,
Durgesh</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Popup for displaying messages (hidden by default) -->
{{> popup}}